link_effecttoeffect4.getReferenceIDs().add(new Reference(link_effecttoeffect4,dataSource,"8.	Simonsson C, Andersson SI, Stenfeldt AL, Bergstrom J, Bauer B, Jonsson CA, Ericson MB, Broo KS. 2011. Caged fluorescent haptens reveal the generation of cryptic epitopes in allergic contact dermatitis. J.Invest. Immunol. 131: 1486-1493. ").<Reference> makeItLive());
